   Seal

       Office of the Law Revision Counsel

     The Office of the Law Revision Counsel prepares and publishes the
     United States Code, which is a consolidation and codification by
     subject matter of the general and permanent laws of the United States.

       * About the Office and the U.S. Code database
       * Search the U.S. Code
       * Download titles and chapters of the U.S. Code or view list of
         titles
       * Classification Tables listing sections of the U.S. Code affected by
         recently enacted laws
       * Codification legislation of the Office
       * Thomas, a legislative service of the Library of Congress
